## Problem
Discovery only probes fixed suffixes `""`, `-p`, `-w`, `-1`, `-2`. Arbitrary dirs like `.claude-work` / `.grok-3` are missed (design table is the same, but real multi-account layouts often use other suffixes). Custom profiles JSON is the only escape hatch and is poorly UX’d.

## Location
contents/scripts/discover-profiles.sh:146-154

## Suggested fix
Glob `.$base*` (with careful filtering) or document supported suffixes prominently in KCM.

